# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository. Without this, Windows
# checkouts (core.autocrlf=true) leave every file showing as CRLF-modified in
# git status even when nothing changed, and tooling churns line endings on
# each `ultracite fix`. Biome formats with `lineEnding: lf`, so LF is the
# single source of truth here.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicitly binary so they're never line-ending converted.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
